# 🏍️ Motorcycle Helmet Deal Finder

Automated daily search for XL modular motorcycle helmets at 40%+ discount across 13 Canadian and international retailers.

## Setup

See SETUP.md in the outputs folder you downloaded for complete instructions.

## What It Does

- Searches daily across FortNine, GP Bikes, ADM Sport, Studio Cycle, RidingGear, Royal Distributing, Champion Helmets, Peakboys, Blackfoot Online, Joe Rocket, Speed & Strength, RevZilla, and Amazon.ca
- Finds deals on: Bell SRT Modular, Shoei Neotec 3, Shoei Neotec 2, HJC RPHA 91, HJC i91, HJC i100, AGV sportmodular, AGV tourmodular, LS2 Advant X, LS2 Advant X 2 Carbon
- Alerts you via email when 40%+ discount deals are found
- Completely automated with GitHub Actions

## Configuration

Add these secrets in Settings → Secrets and Variables → Actions:
- `HELMET_ALERT_EMAIL` - Your email
- `SMTP_USER` - Gmail address
- `SMTP_PASS` - Gmail app password

## Status

View automation status in the **Actions** tab.
